stories.text:
Hello HN! I made a FinTech app called BankShift, with a great team.

I am Looking for responses around super financial apps. e.g. What banking services would you look to build in an all-in-one-app?

Background:

https://BankShift.com has a subscription based model that showcases one login, one app, one, easy-to-use money movement experience. We're also starting to help people save money by finding better terms while gaining credit visibility.

I fell this is the future of banking. However, I have been wrong many time before. :)

Thank you in advance for your time.
